---
import Container from "./Container.astro";
---

<footer class="py-20 md:py-40">
    <Container>
        <div class="m-auto">
            <div class="flex flex-row-reverse flex-wrap items-center justify-between md:flex-nowrap">
                <div class="flex w-full justify-center gap-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 sm:w-7/12 md:justify-start">
                    <ul class="list-inside list-disc space-y-8">
                        <li><a href="#" class="transition hover:text-primary">صفحه نخست</a></li>

                        <li><a href="#" class="transition hover:text-primary">راه حل‌ها</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" class="transition hover:text-primary">درباره من</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" class="transition hover:text-primary">تماس با من</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" class="transition hover:text-primary">بلاگ</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="m-auto mt-16 w-10/12 space-y-6 text-center sm:mt-auto sm:w-5/12 sm:text-right">
                    <div class="flex gap-1 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                        <img width="50" src="/images/logo.svg" />
                        <h5 class="text-xlg">علی نجفی</h5>
                    </div>
                    <span class="block text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"> من به شما در مباحث نرم‌افزار، وب و تکنولوژی کمک میکنم </span>

                    <span class="block text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">به کمک احتیاج دارید؟ <a href="#" class="font-semibold text-gray-600 dark:text-white"> تماس با من</a></span>

                    <span class="block text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">&copy; Ali Najafi <span id="year"></span></span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex text-gray-600">
            <div>
                <a href="https://github.com/alinjf" class="flex items-center space-x-3 transition hover:text-primary">
